  "texts": [
    "Comparably, Salewski et al. [74] enabled the LLMs to assume various roles by introducing the prompt with \"If you were a persona\", in which the target individual is substituted for the persona.",
    "Initial AccessThe initial access tactic includes the procedures adopted by attackers to obtain access as a foothold to a company's infrastructure [90].",
    "Roy et al. [72] highlight the role of LLMs in delivering malicious scripts where the attack structure is divided into four steps.",
    "In this regard, design objects are used to create concepts that are influenced by specific organizations, while credential-stealing objects are used to establish objects that require credentials, including login buttons or input fields.",
    "Credential Transfer objects are used to create functions that can provide the attacker with the credentials submitted on phishing websites."
